{"tid":1825482,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【結束8年情】Vanessa Hudgens與男友Austin分手","createTime":"2020-01-15T10:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T06:31:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b2bec2a9635243b61e058a8e0766251d3d5d3da5","tid":1825482,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T10:09:16.000Z","msg":"31歲《歌舞青春》（High School Musical）美國女星雲妮莎夏芝絲 （Vanessa Hudgens） 正式與28歲男友Austin Butler分手，結束8年情。<br />\n<br />\n據報道指，其實二人早於上年已經傳出情變，但到現在終於正式分開。消息人士指：「雲妮莎與Austin正式分開，女方已經向身邊的朋友公佈消息。」其實二人近月已沒有一起過節，連上月雲妮莎生日，Austin都缺席。近來他們都因工作分隔兩地，雲妮莎正於英國開工，而Austin就忙於澳洲拍攝貓王皮禮士利（Elvis Presley）的傳記電影。雲妮莎曾於2005至2010年與《歌舞青春》拍檔碩克艾佛朗（Zac Efron）拍拖，到2011年9月就開始與Austin拍拖。<br />\n<br />\n然而女方心情似乎未受影響，剛剛更盛裝出席《重案夢幻再重組》（Bad Boys for Life）首映禮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200115/large/1579068837_dc0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200115%2Flarge%2F1579068837_dc0c.jpg&h=460a6ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200115/large/1579068839_1be2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200115%2Flarge%2F1579068839_1be2.jpg&h=fb8e8c52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200115/large/1579068837_93fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200115%2Flarge%2F1579068837_93fb.jpg&h=81d643d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200115/YL3PW3HRHTBQ457MEK7XKVIODA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200115%2FYL3PW3HRHTBQ457MEK7XKVIODA%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=b64afa1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.